  "notes": "The data-video-embed-field-lazy attribute contains raw HTML (an iframe wrapped in a responsive div) that is injected into the DOM when the play button is clicked. The play button (.video-embed-field-lazy-play) is an empty button styled via CSS to show a play icon overlay. The thumbnail image always has loading='lazy'. In the React component, the embedHtml prop should be set as the data-video-embed-field-lazy attribute value on the root div. The actual play/swap behaviour is handled by a Drupal JS library and is outside the scope of this component.",
